<li>Iacocca, Lee and William Novak (1986 reissue). <i><a href="/wiki/Iacocca:_An_Autobiography" title="Iacocca: An Autobiography">Iacocca: An Autobiography</a></i>. Bantam. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0553251470" class="internal">ISBN 0553251470</a></li>
</ul>
